  <section class="article__content">
    

    

    
      <p>We have updated our default Jekyll version from 3.3.0 to 3.3.1, to match the <a href="https://github.com/blog/2290-relative-links-for-github-pages">recent update at GitHub Pages</a>.</p>

<p>This update includes a few minor enhancements and bug fixes. For a full list of revisions <a href="https://jekyllrb.com/docs/history/#v3-3-1">check out the release notes</a>.</p>

<p>Also included in this update are two new <a href="https://learn.siteleaf.com/themes/jekyll-plugins/">whitelisted plugins</a>.</p>

    
    
